\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Motivating example of RouteRec. Different users and sessions can exhibit different behavioral characteristics, suggesting that they need not share the same computation path. RouteRec addresses this by extracting compact behavioral cues from simple sequential signals and using them as explicit routing signals.}}{1}{figure.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
